=== 1. EXECUTION: ===

To compile the program, on the terminal enter the following commands:

	qmake -project QT+=widgets
	qmake
	make

To run the program, on the terminal enter the following command:

	./a3

=== 2. PROGRAM USE: ===

Load a texture first
then load a model
texture will be applied

if you load a model before texture, you wont be able to load texture due to a bug in QFileDialog and you will be see your model as black

== 3. ALGORITHMS and DESIGN DECISIONS: ===

Face normal calculated via algorithm discussed in class. That is take vertices. amke vector from it. Take cross product of the two vertices. normalize them

Vertex normal calculated via algorithm discussed in class. that is take a vertex, find all adjacent faces. take their normals sum them up and divide it my number of faces.

